{
  "texts": [
    "Pathologist 2, on the other hand, prefers the AI-generated report for BMN 80% of the time.",
    "The AI-generated report for SK is preferred by both pathologists 90% of the time.",
    "Across all 100 report pairs, both pathologists find no difference between the generated and human reports about 45% of the time and prefer the AI-generated reports about 15% of the time (see Figure 3D).",
    "According to a post-analysis provided by the two pathologists, after about 20 cases, they were able to tell which report was likely generated by the AI and which was likely generated by a human pathologist.",
    "The AI-generated text tends to be more structured and comprehensive."
  ]
}